init_text: When you die, you appear in a cinema with a number of other people who look like you. You find out that they are your previous reincarnations, and soon you all begin watching your next life on the big screen.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The film is about your life, and you are the star.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You all agree that you are in a cinema, and that you are watching a film about your lives.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You watch as you are born, and then grow up.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You watch as you make your first love, and then your first heartbreak.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You watch as you go through the same experiences again and again, and you begin to wonder if you are really making any progress.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You return to your seat, and continue watching the film.
